Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經有一個世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once there was a world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它與我們的星球沒什麼不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not so very different from our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾會有些自然災害或者是大規模的火山爆發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were occasional natural catastrophes, massive volcanic eruptions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,時不時還會有小行星降臨在星球上砸幾個坑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, every once in a while, an asteroid would come barreling out of the blue to do some damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可在最初的100萬年裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for the first billion years or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它很像是一個天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would've seemed like a paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這大概就是金星在太陽系還年輕時的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what we think the planet Venus might have looked like when our solar system was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 一切就開始變得糟糕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then things started to go horribly wrong.
